posts.cooked: I download the photonvision-v2023.1.2-winx64.jar to my computer after I wanted to upgrade the version from 5 beta. after I downloaded the jar file it didn’t update in the photonvision Dashboard. what should I do?
Download the.jar, do Java -jar [path to jar], and then open up the web dashboard. Might have to do a force refresh.
